Odette Talazac https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Odette_Talazac 0 Odette Talazac (1883–1948) was a French film actress.Talazac was the daughter of tenor Jean-Alexandre Talazac and his wife, the soprano Hélène Fauvelle. She began her career singing in music halls before turning to the theater and cinema. She was married in 1900 in Chatou to jeweler Georges Aucoc.
